# PRODUCT REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (PRD)

Project: Safa Selim Portfolio
Version: 2.0
Owner: Safa Selim
Stack: Next.js + TypeScript + Vercel
Architecture: Single Scroll Landing Page
Design Direction: Modern Tech (Dark-First)

------------------------------------------------------------
1. PRODUCT VISION
------------------------------------------------------------

Build a clean, modern, high-performance portfolio that communicates:

• Senior Angular expertise
• Enterprise-scale system experience
• Architecture and state management depth
• Release management leadership
• Technical confidence without gimmicks

The site must feel:
- Structured
- Minimal
- Technical
- Mature
- Fast

No heavy gaming effects.
No cartoon visuals.
No visual noise.

------------------------------------------------------------
2. TARGET AUDIENCE
------------------------------------------------------------

• Recruiters
• Engineering Managers
• Technical Leads
• Enterprise Clients

Primary Goal:
A recruiter should understand the profile within 60 seconds.

------------------------------------------------------------
3. SITE ARCHITECTURE
------------------------------------------------------------

Single Scroll Landing Page Structure:

[Navbar]
[Hero]
[About]
[Experience Timeline]
[Skills]
[Featured Projects]
[Contact]
[Footer]

Navigation scrolls to sections (anchor-based).

------------------------------------------------------------
4. THEME SYSTEM
------------------------------------------------------------

Dark Mode: Default
Light Mode: Optional toggle

Requirements:

[x] Dark theme default
[x] Light theme toggle in navbar
[x] Detect system preference
[x] Persist user choice in localStorage
[x] Maintain accessibility contrast (WCAG AA)
[x] Ensure animations work in both themes

Color Direction:

Dark Background: deep neutral (not pure black)
Light Background: soft off-white (not pure #fff)

Accent Color:
Single modern tech accent (electric blue OR muted cyan OR subtle violet)

No multi-color gradients.
No neon overload.

